<paragraph id="C55757962347D51508CDCF963620228F" pageId="0" pageNumber="47">Central African Republic, Dzanga-Ndoki NP, Lake 1, 8-10.II.2012, SANGHA2012 Team (♂ holotypus) (BMPC); Dzanga-Ndoki NP, Lake 1, 20-23.II.2012 (hand catching and light), SANGHA2012 Team (1♂ paratypus) (BMPC).</paragraph>
